articles.title: Hangzhou Asian Games: Guangdong athletes shine bright, anticipate a glorious performance in Paris Olympics - 羊城晚报
articles.description: Guangdong athletes clinched a total of 30 gold medals, 17 silver medals, and 8 bronze medals, totaling an impressive 55 medals.
